550
01:13:20,270 --> 01:13:23,870
let Mattie stay.'

551
01:13:23,870 --> 01:13:33,230
He went up to Mattie and touched her arm gently.
'I don't, want you to worry, Matt,' he said,

552
01:13:33,230 --> 01:13:41,060
looking down into her eyes with a smile. 'I
guess things will be all right.'

553
01:13:41,060 --> 01:13:49,350
'No, I ain't going to worry,' she said softly.

554
01:13:49,350 --> 01:13:57,440
He went out to the farm, and soon afterwards,
Jotham Powell joined him. As they were doing

555
01:13:57,440 --> 01:14:02,420
their morning's work with the COWS, Jotham
said:

556
01:14:02,420 --> 01:14:10,320
'Mrs Frome told me the new girl's coming'
today, and Mattie's leaving'. I got to take

557
01:14:10,320 --> 01:14:18,950
her down to the station.' Ethan felt the blood
beating in his head. After a moment, he found

558
01:14:18,950 --> 01:14:20,910
his voice, and said:

559
01:14:20,910 --> 01:14:24,840
'Oh, it ain't so sure that Mattie's going
-'

560
01:14:24,840 --> 01:14:35,260
'Is that so?' said Jotham, not at all interested,
and he went on with his work.

561
01:14:35,260 --> 01:14:42,590
When they returned to the kitchen, the two
women were already at breakfast. Zeena was

