583
01:17:22,930 --> 01:17:31,920
sleigh stopped, and Mrs Hale's round, motherly
face looked out. She smiled at Ethan, told

584
01:17:31,920 --> 01:17:36,690
him that her husband was at home, then added:

585
01:17:36,690 --> 01:17:45,190
'I'm sorry that Zeena's feeling bad again.
