587
01:17:54,670 --> 01:18:02,630
When she had gone, Ethan felt less alone in
his unhappiness. It had been a long time since

588
01:18:02,630 --> 01:18:11,160
anyone had spoken to him as kindly as Mrs
Hale. The Hales were caring people who felt

589
01:18:11,160 --> 01:18:18,520
sorry for him, and now he felt sure that they
